Package Application

Class Administrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Administrator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Administrator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class which implements a system administrator, which has an id, name, surname and password. The administrator is not a Registered user because it would work completely different on the graphical user interface.
    Author:
    Javier Delgado del Cerro, Javier Lopez Cano
    See Also:
